<!doctype html>
<html>
  <body style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; color: #111; max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px;">
    <h1 style="font-size: 20px; margin: 0 0 16px;">Your password was changed</h1>
    <p>Hi {{firstName}},</p>
    <p>The password on your account was just changed at <strong>{{occurredAt}}</strong>.</p>
    <p>If this was you, no action is needed.</p>
    <p style="color: #b00; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 24px;">If you didn't change your password, your account may be compromised.</p>
    <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px;">Reset your password immediately and sign out of all devices from your account settings, then contact support if the problem continues.</p>
  </body>
</html>
